
- first run prep-pkg

# debian/prep-pkg ../amdgpu-pro-....tar.xz

- then build the source package

# debuild -S -d

- and push the source to a ppa

- or build locally

# fakeroot debian/rules binary


NOTE: the EULA still prohibits distributing the result:

>>>
